        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/94ad74/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-01-25T18:48:44.801Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Centralized administration (user accounts, permissions, group memberships etc.) are exclusive to managed, non-public solutions. Any organization, incl. and especially government, better be in control of its instant messaging solution at all times, especially in the context of data classification and (the enforcement of) secrecy.</p>",
