        "created_at": "2026-01-27T01:12:13.948Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Tbh the line ‚Äú‚Ä¶the Trump Administration. They‚Äôve proven their immeasurable incompetence beyond a reasonable doubt‚Äù reads as political bashing to me. I couldn‚Äôt care less for American politics but this kind of statement is just not necessary. This community has always been one of straightforward Q&amp;A, testing feedback, and generally helping to make Signal better for everyone. Everything else was fine and did, indeed, contribute to the discussion. Interestingly since this convo began a few days ago, now they‚Äôre breaking the news of multiple signal groups being used by militants and protestors in Minnesota US</p>",
